aces and flexible access to all aspects of a\nmeasurement (input and output signals, and processed data). Our system also\nenables precise control of timing (synchronization of scanning and transport\noperations) and implementation of sophisticated feedback protocols, and thus\nshould be broadly interesting and useful to practitioners in the field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Oct 2014 19:17:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
