lowed measure the time during the day, using\nanalemmatic sundial and at night during the full Moon - with the help of\nmoondial. Keywords: analemmatic sundial, moondial, srubna burial, slab, wells,\ncupped depressions, gnomon, model, technology, astronomical methods,\narchaeoastronomy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Oct 2014 13:08:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Nov 2014 19:22:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2015 04:31:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-28"}
